            . I am a <rs id="t18270111-201-viclabel1116" type="occupation">poulterer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270111-201-victim1874 t18270111-201-viclabel1116"></join>, and live in <placeName id="t18270111-201-crimeloc1117">Great Distaff-lane</placeName>
